text: right St. George's Parish was created as a civil parish in Kings County, Prince Edward Island, Canada, during the 1764-1766 survey of Samuel Holland. It contains the following townships: * Lot 51 * Lot 52 * Lot 53 * Lot 54 * Lot 55 * Lot 56 * Lot 66 It also contains Kings Royalty.
